description: Introducing Giants Planet: Founding Explorers, an exclusive ordinals project that unveils a world of adventure and limitless possibilities. Immerse yourself in the captivating narrative of being the first 222 humans to set foot on Giants Planet. As a holder of Founding Explorers, you are granted a range of exciting benefits and privileges. Prepare to embark on an unparalleled journey that goes beyond imagination.
name: Giants Planet: Founding Explorers
